HEADWORD: Friezed
<hw>Friezed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Gathered, or having
the map gathered, into little tufts, knots, or protuberances. Cf.
<er>Frieze</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>, and <er>Friz</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>,
2.</def>⟦br⟧
